From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mike <michaelgorney4@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 23:02:46 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add/move missing tests

This adds (or moves) the missing conditional-member and urlinclude tests, and changes what's required to make them pass.

